Package: baselines
Type: Package
Title: baselines - a drawing toolbox with visual overlay guides for R graphics (base)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person( given = "Greg", family = "McInerny", email = "g.mcinerny@warwick.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre") )
URL: https://github.com/GregMci/baselines
Maintainer: The package maintainer <g.mcinerny@warwick.ac.uk>
Description: Drawing tools relating to graphics objects and methods which are commonly needed to create and annotate bespoke visualisations. The tools include - 1. Drawing Graphics Within Plots, 2. Drawing Graphics on the Canvas/Device, 3. Simplifying graphics components, 4. Visual queries & 5. Accessible Settings, as well as some Miscellaneous functions.
